<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٢٥٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">ابْنُ بَشَّارٍ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ </a>: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2330">سَعِيدٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5335">أَبِيهِ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a>قَالَ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«ثُمَّ ارْفَعْ حَتَّى تَطْمَئِنَّ جَالِسًا»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>